im a graphic design student at Minerva Art Academy, Groningen. i am curious and always have the desire to learn. i like my designs to be energetic, clear and powerful, sometimes with a fun touch. in my design process i usually take analog as the first approach. experimenting with different mediums and tools helps me get into the flow and gives me free rein to express myself.
it also makes it clear for me as of what steps to take next in order to create a digitalised version.
